        5.45 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0642P0-04045'>
        <a name='S5LV0642P0_20030108_GCR_169'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-daphne-park' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0642P0_20030108_GCR_169' title='Link to this speech by Ms Daphne Park' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
